-- EngrAIm schema v5 — wiki-gap lint, optional semantic recall, and onboarding.
-- No new base tables. Changes are:
--   * meta key 'onboarded' = '1' once a workspace has been onboarded.
--   * (optional) a vec0 virtual table `vec_items(ref TEXT, emb float[N])` created at
--     runtime by the semantic layer IF sqlite-vec + an embedder are available. The core
--     never depends on it; recall falls back to FTS when it's absent.
--   * wiki/_gaps.md is generated by the lint (not a DB object).
